Time":"2017-05-15T22:53:38.000Z","msg":"仲攬住隊垃圾愛貓用咋<br />\n結果一直都打唔到雙極三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48b461cd81e41a50eb1ef5da30a5338e87c3e07","tid":243740,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/063728_085ee3159e470d7adfc9112af0702e58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F063728_085ee3159e470d7adfc9112af0702e58.jpg&h=5b668f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n團長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a75ea2781a73ce091b6a0c8f9de5831c95b643","tid":243740,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲攬住隊垃圾愛貓用咋<br />\n結果一直都打唔到雙極三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凍飲巴打你隊愛貓點組法？"},{"pid":"78f224939b4975ca44713899bc3bf8b47e15c4fa","tid":243740,"uid":56096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg&h=7e037d58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddc940d61c79e4136d6783e366fb7296e8500bcb","tid":243740,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲攬住隊垃圾愛貓用咋<br />\n結果一直都打唔到雙極三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凍飲巴打你隊愛貓點組法？</blockquote><br />\n愛貓 舊木印 新木印 玄武 群馬縣<br />\n繼咗木賢龍，破防，減傷盾，其他亂嚟<br />\n<br />\n其實都夠打好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最難嗰啲要求真係高好多"},{"pid":"e05be2a192f1b87c690a60f36c811d8bbbc2ccac","tid":243740,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg&h=7e037d58&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解個個都咁多白虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae5fae8ebf87a58d1d0fef16fb84ced579fd732","tid":243740,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg&h=7e037d58&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解個個都咁多白虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩咗千幾日都係得一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0c2effb4fa55c70c1397dad0a3d8c33be755e0","tid":243740,"uid":59838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F065946_a57262dbae475eac5a268a0b9d7a85bd.jpg&h=7e037d58&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解個個都咁多白虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /