6nmt&h=fb1bc650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我其撚玩依隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/074333_08f8a2ccfc64feb45eaf844f00daa476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F074333_08f8a2ccfc64feb45eaf844f00daa476.jpg&h=eab12446&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"179154ed4bdb5a5fcd7a7cba5d20ae56694d0444","tid":243740,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T23:57:44.000Z","msg":"最近用呢隊配團長過雙極3 都幾輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n有五色就可以無視防禦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/074653_5f15895c1544aaa3bffa9886a61398a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F074653_5f15895c1544aaa3bffa9886a61398a5.jpg&h=d6523a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n技能我就選擇咁安裝<br />\n<br />\n鏖魔 放稻田 關鍵時刻+1combo<br />\n<br />\n白虎放風神，對吸傷盾<br />\n<br />\n王子放減傷 保命，覺得唔洗咁保命 可以考慮換6色陣<br />\n<br />\n暗雅我放返暗雅，有Buff三圍，冇雙暗雅或者直接落多隻大蛇用<br />\n<br />\n最後月讀放6色陣 確保返打雙極3 mp龍轉到5色<br />\n咁就可以破防直接秒<br />\n<br />\n最近del左好多無上線既人，有興趣加個好友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n191414617<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/074935_cac8fcc74e43e8544f0956101186fd95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F074935_cac8fcc74e43e8544f0956101186fd95.jpg&h=d5aed181&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/074936_36c33ac4f40264e7fccd10d6b8d34ab3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F074936_36c33ac4f40264e7fccd10d6b8d34ab3.jpg&h=1bbcc81a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/074937_36c33ac4f